reviews.review_text: Blow Away ! being mind blowing is what I remember most about this show.

Good show missed the encore because I was hauled away with people who got caught videotaping the show.

The first west coast Help/slip/frank was great. Blow Away, as usual, fantastic energy.

Get all 3 nights if you can

SHOWTIME Great times at these shows @ the Forum in the midst of the fab Lakers running their "Showtime" fast-breakin offense...all the freaks crawling around Inglewood.  Brent is on top of his game during this run...  lotsa Magic in everybody's crazy fingers!
My First Show The balloon guy was there, very trippy show...fell in love with the dead at this show...You're right very "mind blowing"
